
=== How to connect the camera, camera controller and computer together  ===

==== Objects needed ====

*1x USB 3.0 Type A to B Cable (included in the camera package)
*1x Hamamatsu ORCA-FLASH4.0 AC power cable (included in the camera package)

==== Tools needed ====

none

==== Description ====

The Hamamatsu Orca ER camera controller communicates with the computer via Firewire. Connect the Firewire Type 1 plug into the camera controller's Type 1 jack and the Type B plug on the other end into the computer's Type B jack. Next, connect the camera controller to the camera via the D50 serial cable.

